{"id":130712,"date":"2023-07-20T08:55:10","date_gmt":"2023-07-20T08:55:10","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/?p=130712"},"modified":"2023-07-20T09:15:26","modified_gmt":"2023-07-20T09:15:26","slug":"the-financial-commission-launches-new-free-education-portal-for-retail-fx-and-cfd-traders","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/2023\/07\/20\/the-financial-commission-launches-new-free-education-portal-for-retail-fx-and-cfd-traders\/","title":{"rendered":"The Financial Commission Launches New Free Education Portal for Retail FX and CFD Traders\u00a0","gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"text"}]},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Financial Commission, a leading independent, non-governmental self-regulatory organization and external dispute resolution (EDR) forum, announces the launch of a new, <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/traders-education\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">free education portal<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0for retail FX and CFD traders on its <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">official website<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> as part of its ongoing efforts to educate traders on a variety of topics related to trading financial markets, including managing trading risks, thus <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">contributing to their overall knowledge about Forex trading.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The new portal, launched in partnership with <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.traders-education.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Traders-Education<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, features video tutorials and e-books covering popular financial markets, including Forex, CFDs, commodities, and stocks. Traders can also access a robust glossary of market and trading industry terms, analyze market prices and news from different regions, and review crucial upcoming economic news releases via the calendar.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-130731 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/\u0421\u043d\u0438\u043c\u043e\u043a-\u044d\u043a\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0430-2023-07-20-\u0432-11.47.48.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2382\" height=\"1318\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/\u0421\u043d\u0438\u043c\u043e\u043a-\u044d\u043a\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0430-2023-07-20-\u0432-11.47.48.png 2382w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/\u0421\u043d\u0438\u043c\u043e\u043a-\u044d\u043a\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0430-2023-07-20-\u0432-11.47.48-300x166.png 300w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/\u0421\u043d\u0438\u043c\u043e\u043a-\u044d\u043a\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0430-2023-07-20-\u0432-11.47.48-1024x567.png 1024w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/\u0421\u043d\u0438\u043c\u043e\u043a-\u044d\u043a\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0430-2023-07-20-\u0432-11.47.48-768x425.png 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/\u0421\u043d\u0438\u043c\u043e\u043a-\u044d\u043a\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0430-2023-07-20-\u0432-11.47.48-1536x850.png 1536w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/\u0421\u043d\u0438\u043c\u043e\u043a-\u044d\u043a\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0430-2023-07-20-\u0432-11.47.48-2048x1133.png 2048w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/\u0421\u043d\u0438\u043c\u043e\u043a-\u044d\u043a\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0430-2023-07-20-\u0432-11.47.48-830x459.png 830w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/\u0421\u043d\u0438\u043c\u043e\u043a-\u044d\u043a\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0430-2023-07-20-\u0432-11.47.48-230x127.png 230w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/\u0421\u043d\u0438\u043c\u043e\u043a-\u044d\u043a\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0430-2023-07-20-\u0432-11.47.48-350x194.png 350w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/\u0421\u043d\u0438\u043c\u043e\u043a-\u044d\u043a\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0430-2023-07-20-\u0432-11.47.48-480x266.png 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2382px) 100vw, 2382px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Likewise, traders can learn the important basics of how to conduct technical and fundamental market analysis, trading psychology, and how to formulate trading strategies using technical indicators.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Traders can also get familiar with popular trading platforms offered by FX and CFD brokers, such as MetaTrader 4, MetaTrader 5, and cTrader, without having to open a trading account.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Everyone can use the <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/traders-education\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">new education portal <\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">for <\/span><b>free<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> simply by submitting their name and email address on the Financial Commission website. Upon registration, users will be able to start using the ebooks, video tutorials, and analysis tools right away.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>About Financial Commission<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Financial Commission has conducted dispute resolution services specifically for FX and CFD traders and broker member firms since 2013 as an independent, non-governmental self-regulatory organization and external dispute resolution (EDR) forum. For more information, <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/about\/what-we-do\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">click here<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> or email us at <\/span><a href=\"mailto:info@financialcommission.org\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">info@financialcommission.org<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The Financial Commission, a leading independent, non-governmental self-regulatory organization and external dispute resolution (EDR) forum, announces the launch of a new, free education portal\u00a0for retail FX and CFD traders on its official website as part of its ongoing efforts to educate traders on a variety of topics related to trading financial markets, including managing trading [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"author":2,"featured_media":36289,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[14,12,15,16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-130712","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-commission-news","category-company-news-news-events","category-press-release","category-press-releases-news-events"],"acf":[],"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"link","format":"url"}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/130712","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=130712"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/130712\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":130756,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/130712\/revisions\/130756"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{